<form
        class="auth__form"
        @submit.prevent="submit"
>
    <form-input
            v-model.trim="username"
            :label="$t('auth.user')"
            :v="v.username"
            :autofocus="true"
    ></form-input>

    <form-input
            class="form__input"
            v-model.trim="password"
            :label="$t('auth.password')"
            :v="v.password"
            :type="'password'"
    ></form-input>

    <form-input
            v-model.trim="confirmPassword"
            :label="$t('auth.confirmPassword')"
            :v="$v.confirmPassword"
            :type="'password'"
    ></form-input>

    <form-input
            v-model.trim="certificate"
            :label="$t('auth.key')"
            :v="v.certificate"
    ></form-input>

    <btn
            class="btn form__button"
            type="submit"
            :disabled="computeDisabled"
    >
        {{computeButton}}
    </btn>
</form>
